@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8002
@pipelineId = 6d649347-f2b5-4695-bf74-d50b89764811
@checkpointId = replace-with-checkpoint-id

### 创建 Pipeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requirement_raw": "我要做一个简单的待办事项管理系统，支持增删改查待办，设置待办完成状态，前端页面要好看，后端用Python FastAPI开发"
}

### 列出所有 Pipelines
GET {{baseUrl}}/pipelines

### 启动 Pipeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}/run
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 仅执行已接入 Agent 的阶段（推荐逐步测试时使用）
POST {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}/run-agent-stages
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 自动推进到结束（已接入 agent 的阶段会自动执行，其余阶段走审批流）
POST {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}/auto-advance
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 单步推进一个 Stage（兼容接口：若当前阶段已接入 agent，会优先自动执行 agent）
POST {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}/advance-one-stage
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询 Pipeline 状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}

### 查询当前 Stage
GET {{baseUrl}}/pipelines/{{pipelineId}}/current-stage

### Approve Checkpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkpoints/{{checkpointId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"note": "approved from http file"
}

### Reject Checkpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkpoints/{{checkpointId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"note": "rejected from http file"
}